- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with the use of deep learning techniques for shape retrieval. 
- cs.GR (Graphics) is a possible category as the paper deals with 3D shapes and their representation. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is also a possible category as the paper deals with large-scale shape retrieval using neural networks.
